list.title: Black Frames
list.product_info:
Put your memories on display in the most simply beautiful way. Our Everyday Memories frame adds a picture-perfect finishing touch to any room. Just choose the perfect size and color to complement your favorite photo!

  • Strikingly simple, eye-catching frame complements any décor
  • Available in black, white, espresso or light rustic gray
  • Made of durable MDF wood with a wood-grain effect
  • Beautifully displays one 4” x 6” photo on a table or desk; wall options available as well
  • Create a gallery-style look with a printed matte (larger frames only)
  • Variety of sizes available
